meo]]<ref name=\"KBA list\" />\n|- align=center\n| ZCF\n| Italy\n| [[Iveco]]<ref name=\"KBA list\" />\n|- align=center\n| ZFA\n| Italy\n| [[Fiat Automobiles|Fiat]]<ref name=\"KBA list\" />\n|- align=center\n| ZFF\n| Italy\n| [[Ferrari]]<ref name=\"KBA list\" />\n|- align=center\n| ZGA\n| Italy\n| [[Iveco|IvecoBus]]<ref name=\"KBA list\" />\n|- align=center\n| ZHW\n| Italy\n| [[Lamborghini]]<ref name=\"KBA list\" />\n|- align=center\n| ZLA\n| Italy\n| [[Lancia]]<ref name=\"KBA list\" />\n|- align=center\n| 1B\n| United States\n| [[Dodge]]<ref name=\"KBA list\" />\n|- align=center\n| 1C\n| United States\n| [[Chrysler]]<ref name=\"KBA list\" />\n|- align=center\n| 1F\n| United States\n| [[Ford Motor Company|Ford]]<ref name=\"KBA list\" />\n|- align=center\n| 1G\n| United States\n| [[General Motors]]<ref name=\"KBA list\" />\n|- align=center\n| 1G1\n| United States\n| [[Chevrolet]]\n|- align=center\n| 1G3\n| United States\n| [[Oldsmobile]]\n|- align=center\n| 1G4\n| United States\n| [[Buick]]<ref name=\"GM 2016\" />\n|- align=center\n| 1G9\n| United States\n| [[Google]]\n|- align=center\n| 1GB\n| United States\n| Chevrolet incomplete vehicles<ref name=\"GM 2016\">{{cite web |title=Revision to General Motors\u2019 Vehicle Identification Number decoding for 2016 Model Year |url=ftp://ftp.nhtsa.dot.gov/mfrmail/ORG10560.pdf |publisher=National Highway Traffic Safety Administration |location=US |date=2015-01-12 |access-date=2019-03-13}}</ref> \n|- align=center\n| 1GC\n| United States\n| [[Chevrolet]]\n|- align=center\n| 1GD\n| United States\n| GMC incomplete vehicles<ref name=\"GM 2016\"/>\n|- align=center\n| 1GM\n| United States\n| [[Pontiac]]\n|- align=center\n| 1HG\n| United States\n| [[Honda]]<ref name=\"KBA list\" />\n|- align=center\n| 1J\n| United States\n| [[Jeep]]<ref name=\"KBA list\" />\n|- align=center\n| 1L\n| United States\n| [[Lincoln Motor Company|Lincoln]]<ref name=\"KBA list\" />\n|- align=center\n| 1M\n| United States\n| [[Mercury (automobile)|Mercury]]<re