| 6F\n| Australia\n| [[Ford Motor Company|Ford]]<ref name=\"KBA list\" />\n|- align=center\n| 6G\n| Australia\n| [[General Motors]]\n|- align=center\n| 6G1\n| Australia\n| [[Chevrolet]]\n|- align=center\n| 6G2\n| Australia\n| [[Pontiac]]\n|- align=center\n| 6H\n| Australia\n| [[Holden]]\n|- align=center\n| 6MM\n| Australia\n| [[Mitsubishi Motors|Mitsubishi]]<ref name=\"KBA list\" />\n|- align=center\n| 6T1\n| Australia\n| [[Toyota]]\n|- align=center\n| 6U9\n| Australia\n| Japanese Imports<ref>{{cite web |title=Importing vehicles without a 17 character VIN |url=https://infrastructure.gov.au/vehicles/imports/vins.aspx |website=NEVDIS}}</ref>\n|- align=center\n| 7A1\n| New Zealand\n| [[Mitsubishi Motors|Mitsubishi]]\n|- align=center\n| 7A3\n| New Zealand\n| [[Honda]]\n|- align=center\n| 7A4\n| New Zealand\n| [[Toyota]]\n|- align=center\n| 7A5\n| New Zealand\n| [[Ford Motor Company|Ford]]\n|- align=center\n| 7A8\n| New Zealand\n| [[NZ Transport Agency]] (pre-2009)\n|- align=center\n| 7AT\n| New Zealand\n| [[NZ Transport Agency]] (post-2009)\n|- align=center\n| 8AP\n| Argentina\n| [[Fiat]]\n|- align=center\n| 8AF\n| Argentina\n| [[Ford]]<ref name=\"KBA list\" />\n|- align=center\n| 8AG\n| Argentina\n| [[General Motors]]\n|- align=center\n| 8AW\n| Argentina\n| [[Volkswagen]]\n|- align=center\n| 8AJ\n| Argentina\n| [[Toyota]]\n|- align=center\n| 8A1\n| Argentina\n| [[Renault]]\n|- align=center\n| 8AC\n| Argentina\n| [[Mercedes Benz]]\n|- align=center\n| 8BC\n| Argentina\n| [[Citro\u00ebn]]\n|- align=center\n| 8AD\n| Argentina\n| [[Peugeot]]\n|- align=center\n| 8C3\n| Argentina\n| [[Honda]]\n|- align=center\n| 8AT\n| Argentina\n| [[Iveco]]\n|- align=center\n| 9BD\n| Brazil\n| [[Fiat Autom\u00f3veis]]\n|- align=center\n| 9BG\n| Brazil\n| [[General Motors]]\n|- align=center\n| 9BW\n| Brazil\n| [[Volkswagen]]<ref name=\"KBA list\" />\n|- align=center\n| 9BF\n| Brazil\n| [[Ford]]\n|- align=center\n| 93H\n| Brazil\n| [[Honda]]\n|- align=center\n| 9BR\n| Brazil\n| [[Toyota]]\n|- align=center\n| 936\n| Brazil\n| [[Peugeot]]\n|- align=center\n| 935\n| Brazil\n| [[Citro\u00ebn]]\n|- align=center\n| 93Y\n| Brazil\n| [[Renault]]\n|- align=center\n| 93X\n| Brazil\n| Souza Ramos - Mitsubishi / Suzuki\n|- align=center\n| 9BH\n| Brazil\n| [[Hyundai Motor Company|Hyundai]]\n|- align=center\n| 95P\n| Brazil\n| [[w:pt:Grupo Caoa|CAOA / Hyundai]]\n|- align=center\n| 94D\n| Brazil\n| [[Nissan]]\n|- align=center\n| 94N\n| Brazil\n| RWM Brazil\n|- align=center\n| 98R\n| Brazil\n| [[Chery]]\n|- align=center\n| 988\n| Brazil\n| [[Jeep]]\n|- align=center\n| 98M\n| Brazil\n| [[BMW]]\n|- align=center\n| 9BM\n| Brazil\n| [[Mercedes-Benz]]\n|- align=center\n| 99A\n| Brazil\n| [[Audi]]\n|- align=center\n| 99J\n| Brazil\n| [[Jaguar Land Rover]]\n|- align=center\n| 9C2\n| Brazil\n| [[Honda Motorcycles]]<ref name=\"KBA list\" />\n|- align=center\n| 9C6\n| Brazil\n| [[Yamaha]]<ref name=\"KBA list\" />\n|- align=center\n| 9CD\n| Brazil\n| [[Suzuki|Suzuki (motorcycles)]]\n|- align=center\n| 93W\n| Brazil\n| [[Fiat Professional]]\n|- align=center\n| 93Z\n| Brazil\n| [[Iveco]]\n|- align=center\n| 953\n| Brazil\n| [[Volkswagen Caminh\u00f5es e \u00d4nibus|VW Trucks / MAN]]\n|- align=center\n| 9BS\n| Brazil\n| [[Scania]]\n|- align=center\n| 9BV\n| Brazil\n| [[Volvo Trucks]]\n|- align=center\n| 9FB\n| Colombia\n| [[Renault]]\n|- align=center\n| 9UJ\n| Uruguay\n| [[Chery]]\n|- align=center\n| 9UK\n| Uruguay\n| [[Lifan Group|Lifan]]\n|- align=center\n| 9UW\n| Uruguay\n| [[Kia]]\n|- align=center\n|}\n\n==See also==\n* [[Builder's plate]]\n* [[Danish bicycle VIN-system]]\n* [[Engine number]]\n* [[Name plate]]\n* [[Serial number]]\n* [[VIN etching]]\n* [[RPO Code]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{wikibooks|Vehicle Identification Numbers (VIN codes)}}\n{{Commons category|Vehicle Identification Number}}\n<!--======================== {{No more links}} ============================\n    | PLEASE BE CAUTIOUS IN ADDING MORE LINKS TO THIS ARTICLE. Wikipedia  |\n  